[2026-03-04]
- User report: `Add Module` / `Add Command` buttons do nothing in dedicated config page.
- Root cause identified in `src/etrax/standalone/token_ui.py`:
  - Embedded JavaScript is rendered from a Python f-string template.
  - Regex/string literals for newline handling were not safely escaped for f-string rendering in prior state, which broke generated script syntax and prevented button event handlers from executing.
- Updated `src/etrax/standalone/token_ui.py`:
  - Ensured JS newline literals are escaped in template source:
    - `.split(/\\r?\\n/)`
    - `.join("\\n")`
  - This keeps rendered client-side script valid and restores command/module editor interactions.
